Element.waitUntilClicked                     is this correct? If so then must be a Condition, etc...
Element.waitUntilDoubleClicked               is this correct? If so then must be a Condition, etc...

Element.isElementPresent must call Element.waitUntilIsElementPresent
Element.areElementsPresents must call Element.waitUntilAreElementsPresents

Driver.isElementPresent must call Driver.waitUntilIsElementPresent
Driver.areElementsPresents must call Driver.waitUntilAreElementsPresents